   Wijayanto, Rudi Purwo, Inst Teknol Indonesia, Mech Engn Dept, South Tangerang 15314, Indonesia.
   Fithri, Silvy Rahmah, IPB Univ, Dept Geophys \& Meteorol, Study Program Adv Climatol, Bogor 16143, Indonesia.},
DOI = {10.1016/j.rsase.2026.101909},
