   Li, Xi, Wuhan Univ, State Key Lab Informat Engn Surveying Mapping \& Re, Wuhan 430079, Hubei, Peoples R China.
   Wang, Yiguo, Nansen Environm \& Remote Sensing Ctr, N- 5004 Bergen, Norway.},
