   Huang, Junpeng; Zhang, Zizhao; Shi, Guangming; Zhang, Yanyang; Chen, Kai, Xinjiang Univ, State Key Lab Geomech \& Deep Underground Engn, Urumqi 830017, Peoples R China.
   Ling, Sixiang, Southwest Jiaotong Univ, Fac Geosci \& Engn, Chengdu 61175, Peoples R China.},
DOI = {10.1016/j.asr.2025.08.014},
