Affiliation = {Toure, M (Corresponding Author), Agence Natl Aviat Civile \& Meteorol ANACIM, BP 8184, Dakar, Senegal.
   Toure, Mory, Agence Natl Aviat Civile \& Meteorol ANACIM, BP 8184, Dakar, Senegal.
