   Zhang, Jiang; Xiao, Changlai; Liang, Xiujuan; Yang, Weifei; Zhang, Linzuo; Dai, Rongkun; Li, Weifeng, Natl Local Joint Engn Lab Insitu Convers Drilling, Changchun 130021, Peoples R China.
