Abstract = {The machine learning technique is a computational algorithm that is
   currently developing and is widely used in various models because it has
   the advantage of predicting without limited assumptions. Therefore, the
   purpose of this research is to develop a machine learning method on the
   kriging interpolation method to overcome the unmet assumptions of
