   Rehman, Adnanul, Henan Univ, Key Res Inst Yellow River Civilizat \& Sustainable, Coll Geog \& Environm Sci, Kaifeng 475004, Peoples R China.
   Rehman, Adnanul, Henan Univ, Collaborat Innovat Ctr Yellow River Civilizat Hen, Kaifeng 475004, Peoples R China.
   Bindajam, Ahmed Ali, King Khalid Univ, Coll Architecture \& Planning, Dept Architecture, Abha 61411, Saudi Arabia.
