   Wu, Shiwen, North China Univ Water Resources \& Elect Power, Coll Surveying \& Geoinformat, Zhengzhou 450046, Peoples R China.
   Ma, Yuxin, Manaaki Whenua Landcare Res, Manawatu Mail Ctr, Private Bag 11052, Palmerston North 4442, New Zealand.},
DOI = {10.1016/j.geoderma.2024.117031},
