   noting that the application of the PSO algorithm significantly enhanced
   the model's performance. Additionally, it's crucial to highlight that
   approximately 25 \% of the study region exhibits a high to very high
   susceptibility to flood events. Taking into account the very precise
   results of the models applied in the present study, we can state that
   from a hydrological point of view, the current research contributes to a
   better},
