   Mushagalusa, Ciza Arsene; Kakai, Romain Glele, Univ Abomey Calavi, Fac Sci Agron, Lab Biomath \& Estimat Forestieres, 04 PB 1525, Cotonou, Benin.
   Mushagalusa, Ciza Arsene, Univ Evangel Africa UEA, Fac Agr \& Environm Sci, Bukavu 3323, DEM REP CONGO.
