   Bai, Xueyuan, China Agr Univ, Coll Resources \& Environm, Beijing 100193, Peoples R China.
   Li, Xuecao, China Agr Univ, Coll Land Sci \& Technol, Beijing 100193, Peoples R China.
   Wang, Pengxin; Hu, Yuchen; Zhang, Jie, Minist Agr \& Rural Affairs, Key Lab Agr Machinery Monitoring \& Big Data Applic, Beijing 100083, Peoples R China.
   Lyu, Yujiao; Zhang, Jie, Natl Innovat Ctr Digital Agr Prod Circulat, Beijing 100083, Peoples R China.},
