   Yang, Wantao; Zhang, Liankai; Zhang, Ya; Li, Qiang, China Geol Survey, Kunming Gen Survey Nat Resources Ctr, Kunming 650111, Peoples R China.
   Yang, Wantao; Zhang, Liankai; Liu, Xiaojie; Zhang, Ya; Li, Qiang, Minist Nat Resources, Technol Innovat Ctr Nat Ecosyst Carbon Sink, Kunming 650111, Peoples R China.
   Gao, Bingbo; Wang, Chenyi, China Agr Univ, Coll Land Sci \& Technol, 17 Tsinghua East Rd, Beijing 100083, Peoples R China.},
