   Suleymanov, Azamat, Ufa State Petr Technol Univ, Dept Environm Protect \& Prudent Exploitat Nat Reso, Ufa 450064, Russia.
   Kuzmenko, Petr, Voeikov Main Geophys Observ, Dept Geophys Monitoring \& Res, Karbysheva St 7, St Petersburg 194021, Russia.
