Affiliation = {Wanghe, K; Zhao, K (Corresponding Author), Chinese Acad Sci, Northwest Inst Plateau Biol, Key Lab Adaptat \& Evolut Plateau Biota, Lab Plateau Fish Evolutionary \& Funct Genom,Qingha, Xining, Peoples R China.
