   Brenning, Alexander, Michael Stifel Ctr Jena Data Driven \& Simulat Sci, Jena, Germany.
   Grupp, Veronika, Univ Leipzig, Inst Earth Syst Sci \& Remote Sensing, Leipzig, Germany.},
