   Maneechot, Luksanaree; Wong, Yong Jie; Shimizu, Yoshihisa; Bharambe, Khagendra Pralhad, Kyoto Univ, Res Ctr Environm Qual Management, Grad Sch Engn, Kyoto, Japan.
   Wong, Yong Jie; Ram-Indra, Teerawat, Kyoto Univ Adv Sci, Fac Bioenvironm Sci, Dept Bioenvironm Design, Kameoka 6068501, Japan.
   Try, Sophal, Kyoto Univ, Disaster Prevent Res Inst, Gokasho, Uji 6110011, Japan.
