   Shatnawi, Rania, Al Hussein Tech Univ, Sch Built Environm Engn, Dept Civil Engn, Amman 11822, Jordan.
   Al-Shabeeb, Abdel Rahman; Al-Adamat, Rida, Al al Bayt Univ, Fac Earth \& Environm Sci, Dept Geog Informat Syst \& Remote Sensing, Mafraq 25113, Jordan.
   Al-Amoush, Hani, Al Al Bayt Univ, Fac Earth \& Environm Sci, Dept Appl Earth \& Environm Sci, Mafraq 25113, Jordan.},
