   von Meding, Jason, Univ Florida, Sch Construct Management, Gainesville, FL 32611 USA.
   Nguyen, Lam Phuong; Luu, Chinh, Hanoi Univ Civil Engn, Fac Hydraul Engn, Hanoi 100000, Vietnam.},
