Affiliation = {Liu, YS (Corresponding Author), Northwestern Polytech Univ, Sch Mech Civil Engn \& Architecture, Xian, Peoples R China.
   Fan, Xin; Liu, Yongshou; Guo, Qing; Tian, Weijing, Northwestern Polytech Univ, Sch Mech Civil Engn \& Architecture, Xian, Peoples R China.
