   TECHNIQUES; LANDSCAPE EVOLUTION; PREFERENTIAL FLOW; SOLUTE TRANSPORT;
   ORGANIC-CARBON; BULK-DENSITY; HYDRAULIC CONDUCTIVITY; PEDOTRANSFER
   FUNCTIONS},
