   Kavian, Ataollah, Sari Agr Sci \& Nat Resources Univ, Fac Nat Resources, Sari, Iran.
   Tiefenbacher, John P., Texas State Univ, Dept Geog \& Environm Studies, San Marcos, TX USA.},
