   Uncertainty; Digital soil mapping; Soil-environment relationship; Large
   area; Individual predictive soil mapping (iPSM); Covariates
   applicability; Uncertainty},
Keywords-Plus = {SPATIAL PREDICTION; DIFFERENTIATION; PATTERNS; IMAGERY; REGION; CARBON;
