   ALGORITHM; FUZZY INFERENCE SYSTEM; WEIGHTS-OF-EVIDENCE; SPATIAL
   PREDICTION; RISK-ASSESSMENT; IMPACT ASSESSMENT; HYBRID APPROACH;
   NEURAL-NETWORK},
